=Episode 14=

23
00:01:42,090 --> 00:01:43,110
(Strange.)

24
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:45,010
(Why is Qipei Pavilion's technique)

25
00:01:45,010 --> 00:01:47,140
(so similar to the Crown?)

26
00:01:47,850 --> 00:01:49,420
(Such high aesthetics.)

27
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:50,650
(How could it be trampled underfoot)

28
00:01:50,650 --> 00:01:52,390
(by Suyu Pavilion for so many years?)

29
00:01:55,730 --> 00:01:58,060
(Unless it was drawn
from the real thing.)

30
00:01:58,490 --> 00:01:59,650
(How could it be so detailed)

31
00:01:59,650 --> 00:02:01,500
(in anatomical drawings?)

32
00:02:15,450 --> 00:02:16,310
Mr. Pei.

33
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:19,060
Ms. Shuangshuang,
what are you looking for?

34
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,030
You can ask me directly
if you have any questions.

35
00:02:23,210 --> 00:02:25,500
I'm sorry. It was my rudeness.

36
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:28,030
Young Master,
it's not Ms. Shuangshuang's fault.

37
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,520
Ms. Shuangshuang wanted to study,

38
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,960
so I brought her here.

39
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,750
Don't blame Ms. Shuangshuang.

40
00:02:34,050 --> 00:02:36,190
You're frowning again. Are you angry?

41
00:02:36,490 --> 00:02:38,470
Don't frown. You'll look less handsome.

42
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,090
Ms. Shuangshuang this.

43
00:02:40,090 --> 00:02:41,520
Ms. Shuangshuang that.

44
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,560
Seems like I've spoiled you

45
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,900
too much.

46
00:02:52,890 --> 00:02:54,650
Young Master, I'm sorry.

47
00:02:54,650 --> 00:02:57,430
I asked Liu to bring my sister here.

48
00:02:57,650 --> 00:02:59,220
Taking all the blame.

49
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,380
Even lying.

50
00:03:00,890 --> 00:03:02,370
Do you know what this place is?

51
00:03:02,370 --> 00:03:03,710
How can you bring outsiders here?

52
00:03:09,450 --> 00:03:10,340
Outsiders?

53
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,750
What's wrong with him today?

54
00:03:18,740 --> 00:03:21,580
(Pei's Mansion)

55
00:03:21,580 --> 00:03:25,140
(Peace and Tranquility)

56
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:31,190
Haven't reconciled with Mr. Pei yet?

57
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,470
Reconcile? Only if he comes to me.

58
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:36,620
This was my mistake.

59
00:03:36,890 --> 00:03:38,750
Every family has its privacy,

60
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:41,340
especially since he's your boss.

61
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,870
We servants must learn

62
00:03:43,210 --> 00:03:44,820
to lower our heads.

63
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,620
Shuangshuang,

64
00:03:50,330 --> 00:03:52,780
I have something to tell you.

65
00:03:56,370 --> 00:04:00,310
Actually, I'm with Mr. Pei now.

66
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:03,190
We just haven't told anyone yet.

67
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,380
When did this happen?

68
00:04:07,770 --> 00:04:10,170
So many things happened,

69
00:04:10,170 --> 00:04:13,750
and we ended up together.

70
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,870
Would you oppose it?

71
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:23,790
As long as you're happy,

72
00:04:24,250 --> 00:04:25,910
of course, I won't oppose it.

73
00:04:26,650 --> 00:04:30,500
But do you really know Mr. Pei?

74
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:34,350
I'm afraid you'll get hurt.

75
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,770
Shuangshuang, don't worry.

76
00:04:37,770 --> 00:04:38,810
Though he usually

77
00:04:38,810 --> 00:04:41,130
seems carefree,

78
00:04:41,130 --> 00:04:43,700
he is actually very responsible.

79
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:48,810
Since you're a couple now,

80
00:04:48,810 --> 00:04:50,430
there's no need to be angry at him.

81
00:04:52,210 --> 00:04:55,380
But be careful.

82
00:04:56,090 --> 00:04:57,790
Don't fall too deep.

83
00:04:59,690 --> 00:05:02,110
Trust my judgment, Shuangshuang.

84
00:05:04,330 --> 00:05:05,380
Alright, sit down.

85
00:05:16,780 --> 00:05:17,620
Young Master,

86
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:19,900
it's my fault for taking the library key

87
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:23,420
and making a decision
without your consent.

88
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:25,660
That's why you two are arguing.

89
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:27,540
Please don't be mad at her.

90
00:05:28,340 --> 00:05:30,420
I did say something harsh.

91
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:33,140
I'll apologize to her later.

92
00:05:37,980 --> 00:05:38,820
Young Master,

93
00:05:38,860 --> 00:05:40,580
someone delivered a letter for you.

94
00:05:44,900 --> 00:05:47,500
You were falsely accused of plagiarism
during the Jade Competition.

95
00:05:47,860 --> 00:05:50,980
If you want to clear your name,
let's meet at Flower Pavilion.

96
00:05:51,220 --> 00:05:52,220
Who sent it?

97
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:53,860
I don't know. He left at once.

98
00:06:10,980 --> 00:06:12,540
- Young Master.
- Cuiliu?

99
00:06:16,420 --> 00:06:17,420
Why are you here?

100
00:06:17,740 --> 00:06:19,700
Young Master, I...

101
00:06:20,660 --> 00:06:23,220
Young Master, don't go, please.

102
00:06:23,540 --> 00:06:24,380
Young Master,

103
00:06:24,900 --> 00:06:26,940
I know you don't want to see me.

104
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:29,500
I was bewitched by bad people

105
00:06:29,780 --> 00:06:32,140
and did something stupid.

106
00:06:32,420 --> 00:06:34,540
I deserved to be kicked
out of the Pei family.

107
00:06:34,780 --> 00:06:35,860
But Young Master,

108
00:06:35,860 --> 00:06:37,580
I really know I was wrong.

109
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:41,300
I've been punished.

110
00:06:41,540 --> 00:06:44,180
I did those despicable things

111
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:46,780
out of jealousy.

112
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:49,660
I'm jealous that
Dandan could be by your side.

113
00:06:49,660 --> 00:06:51,300
Young Master, I know I was wrong.

114
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:52,860
Please forgive me.

115
00:06:53,900 --> 00:06:55,700
- Please forgive me, Young Master.
- Fine.

116
00:06:56,420 --> 00:06:57,580
It's good that you know your mistake.

117
00:06:58,460 --> 00:07:00,420
I can change. I definitely can.

118
00:07:01,860 --> 00:07:05,020
I'm no longer part of the Pei family.

119
00:07:05,540 --> 00:07:07,620
I've given up on you.

120
00:07:08,300 --> 00:07:10,740
Tomorrow, I'll leave for my hometown

121
00:07:11,180 --> 00:07:12,460
to be with my parents,

122
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:14,260
get married, have children,

123
00:07:14,660 --> 00:07:15,820
and live the rest of my life.

124
00:07:16,420 --> 00:07:18,180
Today, I came

125
00:07:18,860 --> 00:07:21,540
to see you one last time

126
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:23,140
and serve you one last time.

127
00:07:23,980 --> 00:07:26,980
Let me pour you one last drink

128
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:28,500
and make you one last cup of tea.

129
00:07:49,060 --> 00:07:49,940
Young Master,

130
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:52,620
this might be

131
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:55,180
our last meeting.

132
00:08:02,220 --> 00:08:03,060
Alright.

133
00:08:03,220 --> 00:08:04,700
I have things to do. I'll head back.

134
00:08:40,780 --> 00:08:42,660
Young Master, breakfast is ready.

135
00:08:45,580 --> 00:08:47,860
Young Master, breakfast is ready.

136
00:08:51,190 --> 00:08:52,540
Still angry, huh?

137
00:08:55,260 --> 00:08:57,140
Young Master, breakfast!

138
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:01,780
Young Master!

139
00:09:03,420 --> 00:09:04,540
Where is he?

140
00:09:06,540 --> 00:09:07,740
I was going to ask you the same.

141
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:10,620
Liu,

142
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:18,380
where's Young Master?

143
00:09:19,260 --> 00:09:22,260
He received a letter yesterday

144
00:09:22,260 --> 00:09:24,180
and then rushed out.

145
00:09:24,180 --> 00:09:25,700
He hasn't come back all night?

146
00:09:26,780 --> 00:09:27,780
Where did he go?

147
00:09:28,420 --> 00:09:29,900
How would I know?

148
00:09:29,900 --> 00:09:31,140
Where did he go?

149
00:09:31,140 --> 00:09:32,180
Flower Pavilion.

150
00:09:47,180 --> 00:09:48,340
Wait for me, Dandan.

151
00:09:51,380 --> 00:09:52,500
Take care.

152
00:09:54,700 --> 00:09:56,100
So early today?

153
00:09:56,660 --> 00:09:57,500
What's up?

154
00:09:57,900 --> 00:09:58,780
Where's Pei Pei?

155
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:01,340
Where's Pei Pei?

156
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:03,700
Upstairs, in the private room.

157
00:10:05,540 --> 00:10:07,580
I was only paid for the room.

158
00:10:08,260 --> 00:10:09,180
What?

159
00:10:09,580 --> 00:10:10,940
What's wrong with you?

160
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:12,460
What's with this?

161
00:10:13,780 --> 00:10:14,820
Jerk!

162
00:10:15,380 --> 00:10:17,740
You ruined me.

163
00:10:18,420 --> 00:10:19,660
Jerk!

164
00:10:28,020 --> 00:10:28,860
Young Master.

165
00:10:29,180 --> 00:10:30,060
What's wrong, Young Master?

166
00:10:30,060 --> 00:10:31,420
Wake up, Young Master.

167
00:10:31,700 --> 00:10:33,420
- Young Master, wake up.
- Move.

168
00:10:33,420 --> 00:10:34,540
Look at me, Young Master.

169
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:35,820
Young Master, wake up. Get up.

170
00:10:35,820 --> 00:10:36,780
Take him away. Move.

171
00:10:36,780 --> 00:10:38,180
Get up. Move.

172
00:10:38,180 --> 00:10:39,380
- What's happening, officer?
- Move.

173
00:10:39,780 --> 00:10:40,620
Get up.

174
00:10:41,180 --> 00:10:42,540
Careful, officer.

175
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:13,180
Still not eating?

176
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:20,060
Dandan, eat something.

177
00:11:20,540 --> 00:11:21,540
I have no appetite.

178
00:11:22,180 --> 00:11:23,020
Dandan,

179
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:24,700
eat a little.

180
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:27,860
I don't think

181
00:11:28,380 --> 00:11:30,700
Young Master would
cheat on you with Cuiliu.

182
00:11:31,180 --> 00:11:33,460
Cuiliu is crafty.

183
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:35,340
Don't believe her.

184
00:11:35,540 --> 00:11:37,580
I'm mad at the idiot.

185
00:11:37,580 --> 00:11:39,420
How could he fall for her trick?

186
00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:41,820
Why didn't he tell us before he went out?

187
00:11:42,300 --> 00:11:43,380
And Cuiliu.

188
00:11:44,180 --> 00:11:45,500
She's liked him for a long time.

189
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:47,900
Why would she harm him?

190
00:12:04,780 --> 00:12:06,900
Even the prettiest dragonfly

191
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:08,500
can't fly without wings.

192
00:12:12,180 --> 00:12:13,140
Jue,

193
00:12:14,060 --> 00:12:15,900
three days later, he'll be interrogated.

194
00:12:15,900 --> 00:12:19,100
This time, Pei really can't get away.

195
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:20,260
Indeed.

196
00:12:21,180 --> 00:12:22,500
Coincidentally,

197
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:25,220
a girl appeared at this critical moment,

198
00:12:25,540 --> 00:12:26,660
giving him a hard time.

199
00:12:27,500 --> 00:12:28,340
Coincidentally?

200
00:12:33,260 --> 00:12:34,900
Young Master, she's here.

201
00:12:37,780 --> 00:12:39,380
Congratulations on getting out of prison.

202
00:12:40,540 --> 00:12:41,380
You...

203
00:12:41,660 --> 00:12:43,180
You're Mr. Su.

204
00:12:43,180 --> 00:12:44,580
I heard about your situation.

205
00:12:44,820 --> 00:12:45,740
It's not your fault.

206
00:12:45,940 --> 00:12:47,820
You should blame that unfaithful Pei Pei

207
00:12:47,820 --> 00:12:49,380
and the unruly Shan Dandan.

208
00:12:49,660 --> 00:12:52,420
They forced you to make a grave mistake.

209
00:12:53,820 --> 00:12:54,900
Do you hate them?

210
00:12:56,380 --> 00:12:57,220
Yes.

211
00:12:58,060 --> 00:13:00,020
If you don't mind,
come to Suyu Pavilion.

212
00:13:00,300 --> 00:13:01,660
As long as you're willing to cooperate,

213
00:13:01,900 --> 00:13:03,260
I guarantee you wealth and glory.

214
00:13:07,300 --> 00:13:08,140
What?

215
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:11,420
Do you know why
you were released so quickly?

216
00:13:13,060 --> 00:13:15,020
It was you?

217
00:13:15,260 --> 00:13:16,900
You and I were both wronged.

218
00:13:17,300 --> 00:13:19,180
Don't you want to make those two

219
00:13:19,180 --> 00:13:20,380
suffer?

220
00:13:20,820 --> 00:13:21,860
Or do you want

221
00:13:22,780 --> 00:13:24,660
to end up on the streets?

222
00:13:29,660 --> 00:13:32,180
What do you want me to do?

223
00:13:35,660 --> 00:13:38,220
Good move, using her against Pei Pei.

224
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:40,780
It's his fault.

225
00:13:40,780 --> 00:13:42,500
He wasn't careful

226
00:13:42,820 --> 00:13:44,900
to have so many people resent him.

227
00:13:44,900 --> 00:13:47,380
Jue, you finally get it.

228
00:13:47,580 --> 00:13:48,580
That's right.

229
00:13:49,060 --> 00:13:51,660
Don't punish yourself
for others' mistakes.

230
00:13:51,660 --> 00:13:52,740
He sowed the seeds.

231
00:13:52,940 --> 00:13:55,220
He should get what he deserves.

232
00:13:55,540 --> 00:13:56,620
You're right.

233
00:13:57,660 --> 00:14:00,140
If there were no Qipei Pavilion,

234
00:14:00,540 --> 00:14:01,980
where would she go?

235
00:14:04,060 --> 00:14:06,300
So now if I ask you for money,

236
00:14:06,300 --> 00:14:08,380
you must give it to me.

237
00:14:10,540 --> 00:14:13,780
If not to bribe the guards,

238
00:14:13,780 --> 00:14:14,620
how can we

239
00:14:14,900 --> 00:14:17,820
make Mr. Pei suffer?

240
00:14:27,300 --> 00:14:28,140
Liu.

241
00:14:28,540 --> 00:14:29,780
What are you doing?

242
00:14:29,780 --> 00:14:31,300
Young Master must have been wronged.

243
00:14:31,300 --> 00:14:32,260
I can't just stand by.

244
00:14:32,260 --> 00:14:33,180
I need to save him.

245
00:14:35,180 --> 00:14:37,060
Do you know what a serious crime
prison raid is?

246
00:14:37,060 --> 00:14:38,660
Even if Mr. Pei is innocent,

247
00:14:38,940 --> 00:14:41,380
your actions will put him in more danger.

248
00:14:41,380 --> 00:14:42,300
So what should I do now?

249
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:43,220
What should I do?

250
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:44,980
We'll all think of a way together.

251
00:14:45,300 --> 00:14:47,620
At this moment, we must not panic.

252
00:14:58,540 --> 00:14:59,380
Alright.

253
00:14:59,780 --> 00:15:00,660
I understand.

254
00:15:01,420 --> 00:15:03,180
I'll need your help

255
00:15:03,180 --> 00:15:04,580
to look after Ms. Dandan.

256
00:15:05,020 --> 00:15:07,660
This incident hit her the hardest.

257
00:15:08,780 --> 00:15:09,700
Of course.

258
00:15:13,780 --> 00:15:14,700
Shopkeeper Hao,

259
00:15:14,700 --> 00:15:15,540
no matter the cost,

260
00:15:15,540 --> 00:15:16,540
try your best

261
00:15:16,540 --> 00:15:17,620
to make connections.

262
00:15:17,820 --> 00:15:18,700
Madam.

263
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:21,420
The best lawyer is on the way.

264
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:24,220
If you want to see him,
it'll be after midnight.

265
00:15:25,780 --> 00:15:26,980
Thank you, officer.

266
00:15:33,060 --> 00:15:33,900
Madam.

267
00:15:37,300 --> 00:15:38,140
Dandan.

268
00:15:38,660 --> 00:15:40,180
- Pei, he...
- I believe him.

269
00:15:41,300 --> 00:15:44,060
I don't believe
he would do such a vile thing.

270
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:46,540
If he coveted Cuiliu,

271
00:15:46,540 --> 00:15:47,940
why wait until now?

272
00:15:53,900 --> 00:15:54,740
Madam,

273
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:56,620
don't worry.

274
00:15:57,060 --> 00:15:58,340
The most important thing now

275
00:15:58,700 --> 00:16:00,180
is to get him out.

276
00:16:00,820 --> 00:16:01,740
Dandan,

277
00:16:03,060 --> 00:16:04,900
I truly didn't misjudge you.

278
00:16:06,780 --> 00:16:07,860
If you need money,

279
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:09,740
go to Shopkeeper Hao directly.

280
00:16:10,140 --> 00:16:11,500
We'll do whatever it takes

281
00:16:12,180 --> 00:16:14,500
to save Pei.

