00:16:17,020 --> 00:16:18,060
And you.

283
00:16:18,060 --> 00:16:19,340
No matter what happens,

284
00:16:19,700 --> 00:16:21,340
be cautious.

285
00:16:21,540 --> 00:16:22,660
Stay safe.

286
00:16:24,540 --> 00:16:25,420
Madam,

287
00:16:26,540 --> 00:16:27,620
don't worry.

288
00:16:28,060 --> 00:16:29,380
I won't let you down.

289
00:16:37,260 --> 00:16:38,100
Trust me.

290
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:43,540
(Prison, Yuncui City)

291
00:16:43,540 --> 00:16:45,340
I'm here to see Pei Pei
of Qipei Pavilion.

292
00:16:47,060 --> 00:16:47,900
Thank you.

293
00:16:49,420 --> 00:16:50,300
Let's go.

294
00:16:52,820 --> 00:16:53,660
He's inside.

295
00:16:54,180 --> 00:16:55,660
- Only for 15 minutes.
- Okay.

296
00:17:19,380 --> 00:17:20,420
Pei Pei?

297
00:17:23,700 --> 00:17:24,540
Pei Pei.

298
00:17:25,540 --> 00:17:26,380
Dandan.

299
00:17:33,980 --> 00:17:35,660
Dandan.

300
00:17:43,020 --> 00:17:44,660
What happened?

301
00:17:46,700 --> 00:17:48,780
Why are you beaten like this?

302
00:17:52,220 --> 00:17:53,140
Does it hurt?

303
00:17:53,580 --> 00:17:54,500
No.

304
00:17:55,620 --> 00:17:57,740
Why did they beat you?

305
00:17:59,300 --> 00:18:01,020
They wanted me to confess.

306
00:18:01,380 --> 00:18:02,820
Of course, I didn't.

307
00:18:03,220 --> 00:18:04,260
So...

308
00:18:06,060 --> 00:18:08,140
They shouldn't beat you anyway.

309
00:18:13,020 --> 00:18:14,980
- Don't cry.
- I know.

310
00:18:14,980 --> 00:18:17,180
I know you were tricked by Cuiliu.

311
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:19,820
I'll find a way to prove your innocence.

312
00:18:20,580 --> 00:18:21,620
Sorry.

313
00:18:22,500 --> 00:18:23,460
I'm so stupid,

314
00:18:23,740 --> 00:18:24,740
making you sad.

315
00:18:24,740 --> 00:18:27,060
How did it come to this?

316
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:32,540
Don't cry.

317
00:18:36,820 --> 00:18:37,860
Hang in there.

318
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:40,180
I'll get you out.

319
00:18:41,860 --> 00:18:42,820
I believe in you.

320
00:18:52,380 --> 00:18:53,220
What?

321
00:18:53,220 --> 00:18:55,060
They dared to torture the young master?

322
00:18:56,860 --> 00:18:57,700
The priority is

323
00:18:58,140 --> 00:19:00,420
to find evidence
and prove his innocence.

324
00:19:00,780 --> 00:19:01,740
The sooner, the better.

325
00:19:05,700 --> 00:19:07,020
But besides us,

326
00:19:07,020 --> 00:19:09,300
how do we prove he was wronged?

327
00:19:20,580 --> 00:19:21,420
Dandan.

328
00:19:22,700 --> 00:19:23,540
What did you find?

329
00:19:24,940 --> 00:19:25,780
They've checked.

330
00:19:25,780 --> 00:19:27,540
They said the wine had no problem.

331
00:19:28,540 --> 00:19:29,380
Of course.

332
00:19:29,780 --> 00:19:31,300
If she really tampered with it,

333
00:19:31,300 --> 00:19:32,900
it would've been cleaned up by now.

334
00:19:34,060 --> 00:19:35,060
Besides Cuiliu,

335
00:19:35,060 --> 00:19:36,420
who else entered the room?

336
00:19:37,220 --> 00:19:39,220
Madam Yang said
it was just the two of them.

337
00:19:40,460 --> 00:19:42,940
Cuiliu has long admired the young master.

338
00:19:43,300 --> 00:19:45,100
If he really did something to her,

339
00:19:45,460 --> 00:19:46,500
she would be happy,

340
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:47,740
instead of acting like that.

341
00:19:48,380 --> 00:19:51,340
Why did she call the young master
to Flower Pavilion?

342
00:19:51,620 --> 00:19:52,980
Who instructed her?

343
00:19:52,980 --> 00:19:54,300
Who reported to the authorities?

344
00:19:55,780 --> 00:19:57,220
There are too many doubts.

345
00:19:57,820 --> 00:20:00,060
Dandan, you must save the young master.

346
00:20:01,300 --> 00:20:02,260
Let me see it too.

347
00:20:06,940 --> 00:20:09,020
(Now that Pei Chufeng
is no longer alive,)

348
00:20:09,500 --> 00:20:11,340
(if Pei Pei is wrongfully imprisoned,)

349
00:20:12,060 --> 00:20:14,060
(I won't be able
to investigate the Crown theft)

350
00:20:14,060 --> 00:20:15,420
(from years ago.)

351
00:20:20,300 --> 00:20:21,540
Shuangshuang, what's wrong?

352
00:20:23,220 --> 00:20:24,060
Nothing.

353
00:20:24,780 --> 00:20:26,980
Let's think of a way to save him.

354
00:20:34,100 --> 00:20:34,940
Your Lordship,

355
00:20:35,140 --> 00:20:37,420
(Xuanzheng Hall)
tomorrow is the trial for Pei Pei's case.

356
00:20:37,700 --> 00:20:40,100
Su Jue paid the fine for Cuiliu

357
00:20:40,100 --> 00:20:42,260
and kept her in Yuncui City.

358
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:44,100
This case is indeed suspicious.

359
00:20:45,380 --> 00:20:47,580
Pei Pei has always been of good character.

360
00:20:47,580 --> 00:20:48,500
He wouldn't do this

361
00:20:48,500 --> 00:20:50,580
unless he's been possessed.

362
00:20:50,820 --> 00:20:52,140
You're right, Your Lordship.

363
00:20:52,540 --> 00:20:54,140
We can't conclude based solely

364
00:20:54,140 --> 00:20:55,260
on Cuiliu's words.

365
00:20:55,980 --> 00:20:57,740
Pei Pei made a mistake,

366
00:20:57,740 --> 00:20:59,820
being manipulated
by Cuiliu multiple times.

367
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:01,820
Have you arranged everyone?

368
00:21:02,860 --> 00:21:04,260
The midwife is ready.

369
00:21:04,500 --> 00:21:06,540
The Pei family knows how to respond.

370
00:21:06,780 --> 00:21:09,020
Tomorrow's trial should reveal the truth.

371
00:21:09,020 --> 00:21:11,140
The Su family is becoming bolder.

372
00:21:11,140 --> 00:21:12,210
We'll teach Su Jue a little lesson

373
00:21:12,210 --> 00:21:14,060
through Pei Pei's case.

374
00:21:14,060 --> 00:21:16,540
The Pei family contributed greatly
to the poison bracelet case.

375
00:21:16,540 --> 00:21:17,380
Besides,

376
00:21:17,380 --> 00:21:18,700
we can punish those

377
00:21:18,700 --> 00:21:20,620
who distort the truth
and fabricate stories.

378
00:21:21,220 --> 00:21:22,500
Go handle it quickly.

379
00:21:22,500 --> 00:21:23,900
Yes, Your Lordship.

380
00:21:28,060 --> 00:21:30,420
(Pei's Mansion)

381
00:21:32,100 --> 00:21:34,620
If Suyu Pavilion indeed bribed Cuiliu

382
00:21:35,060 --> 00:21:36,460
to frame the young master,

383
00:21:37,860 --> 00:21:39,780
this would be troublesome.

384
00:21:41,060 --> 00:21:42,780
The Su family's influence is immense.

385
00:21:43,100 --> 00:21:44,860
They will cover all traces.

386
00:21:45,620 --> 00:21:46,740
Ms. Shuangshuang,

387
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:48,140
you worked at Suyu Pavilion.

388
00:21:48,380 --> 00:21:50,140
Do they really hate
the young master this much?

389
00:21:50,540 --> 00:21:51,420
Well...

390
00:21:52,300 --> 00:21:53,460
It's possible.

391
00:21:53,460 --> 00:21:54,820
Such despicable people.

392
00:21:54,840 --> 00:21:55,700
When they can't compete,

393
00:21:55,700 --> 00:21:57,820
they resort to underhanded tricks.

394
00:21:57,820 --> 00:21:59,380
I want to raid Suyu Pavilion right now.

395
00:21:59,380 --> 00:22:00,220
I'll confront them.

396
00:22:00,240 --> 00:22:01,190
Calm down.

397
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:02,540
Now is not the time to be impulsive.

398
00:22:03,060 --> 00:22:05,140
The most important thing
is to rescue him.

399
00:22:10,460 --> 00:22:11,980
Deputy Shopkeeper, you wanted to see me?

400
00:22:11,980 --> 00:22:13,740
Hongyu, I need to ask you something.

401
00:22:14,380 --> 00:22:16,460
Please answer truthfully.

402
00:22:32,420 --> 00:22:37,060
(Guangju Tavern)

403
00:22:44,100 --> 00:22:48,420
(Guangju Tavern)

404
00:22:50,540 --> 00:22:53,260
Has Cuiliu ever had a lover?

405
00:22:53,940 --> 00:22:54,860
No.

406
00:22:55,620 --> 00:22:56,700
Did she ever

407
00:22:56,700 --> 00:22:58,780
behave improperly with the young master?

408
00:22:58,780 --> 00:23:01,020
Though Cuiliu is somewhat unruly,

409
00:23:01,020 --> 00:23:02,500
she has long admired the young master.

410
00:23:03,020 --> 00:23:04,900
She's inherently traditional.

411
00:23:05,260 --> 00:23:07,060
She wouldn't do such things.

412
00:23:07,380 --> 00:23:08,220
I see.

413
00:23:14,220 --> 00:23:15,100
Hongyu,

414
00:23:15,100 --> 00:23:17,060
take me to Cuiliu's room.

415
00:23:17,060 --> 00:23:17,900
Yes.

416
00:23:24,740 --> 00:23:25,580
Liu,

417
00:23:26,460 --> 00:23:27,700
go to the City Lord,

418
00:23:27,700 --> 00:23:29,020
tell him we have new evidence,

419
00:23:29,780 --> 00:23:31,340
and request a retrial.

420
00:23:31,620 --> 00:23:32,860
- Understood.
- Also,

421
00:23:33,300 --> 00:23:34,620
keep a close watch on Cuiliu.

422
00:23:35,060 --> 00:23:36,380
Make sure nothing happens to her

423
00:23:36,780 --> 00:23:38,060
before the City Lord calls for her.

424
00:23:38,620 --> 00:23:39,460
Got it.

425
00:24:00,540 --> 00:24:02,260
With the key witness Cuiliu found,

426
00:24:02,310 --> 00:24:03,740
(Xuanzheng Hall)
here's the trial for Pei Pei.

427
00:24:04,140 --> 00:24:05,380
Bring Pei Pei in.

428
00:24:26,060 --> 00:24:27,460
Why is Pei Pei injured like this?

429
00:24:27,780 --> 00:24:30,060
He was uncooperative
and refused to confess,

430
00:24:30,060 --> 00:24:31,340
so he was punished.

431
00:24:37,860 --> 00:24:39,700
Your Lordship, Pei Pei is innocent.

432
00:24:40,780 --> 00:24:41,940
Innocent? How so?

433
00:24:42,620 --> 00:24:45,860
That day, I was drugged,

434
00:24:46,140 --> 00:24:47,780
barely conscious.

435
00:24:47,780 --> 00:24:50,500
Today, I can finally speak.

436
00:24:51,780 --> 00:24:54,820
I received an anonymous letter,

437
00:24:55,260 --> 00:24:56,220
saying it could clear my name

438
00:24:56,580 --> 00:24:59,220
in the Jade Competition scandal.

439
00:25:00,860 --> 00:25:01,740
Of course.

440
00:25:03,060 --> 00:25:04,500
Your Lordship, you might not believe

441
00:25:04,500 --> 00:25:05,540
I was framed.

442
00:25:06,340 --> 00:25:07,980
When I arrived at Flower Pavilion,

443
00:25:08,340 --> 00:25:10,620
I found Cuiliu waiting there,

444
00:25:11,100 --> 00:25:12,580
saying she wanted to apologize.

445
00:25:13,060 --> 00:25:14,620
After drinking her wine,

446
00:25:15,060 --> 00:25:16,580
I remembered nothing.

447
00:25:17,260 --> 00:25:19,300
Your Lordship, here's the evidence.

448
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:20,180
Please take a look.

449
00:25:35,300 --> 00:25:37,660
Young Master, heavens!

450
00:25:38,100 --> 00:25:40,260
How could you say such shameless things?

451
00:25:40,540 --> 00:25:42,940
You pretended to be drunk

452
00:25:42,940 --> 00:25:44,540
and defiled me.

453
00:25:44,540 --> 00:25:47,020
How can you wrongfully accuse me?

454
00:25:47,020 --> 00:25:48,500
I think you're the shameless one.

455
00:25:48,740 --> 00:25:49,620
You claim the young master

456
00:25:49,620 --> 00:25:51,340
did something vile to you,

457
00:25:51,340 --> 00:25:52,540
what exactly did he do?

458
00:25:52,540 --> 00:25:53,740
Can you tell us in detail?

459
00:25:53,740 --> 00:25:54,580
I...

460
00:25:56,300 --> 00:25:57,140
I...

461
00:25:58,340 --> 00:26:00,460
Why? Speechless now?

462
00:26:01,540 --> 00:26:02,460
Let me help you.

463
00:26:04,690 --> 00:26:05,540
Your Lordship,

464
00:26:05,540 --> 00:26:08,100
I request the midwife
to assist in the investigation.

465
00:26:08,100 --> 00:26:08,940
Granted.

466
00:26:13,060 --> 00:26:14,540
Greetings, Your Lordship.

467
00:26:14,540 --> 00:26:16,180
This is a renowned midwife
in Yuncui City,

468
00:26:16,380 --> 00:26:18,900
expert at determining
if a woman is a virgin.

469
00:26:19,100 --> 00:26:20,260
She has never failed.

470
00:26:20,260 --> 00:26:22,020
Since Cuiliu claims such a great insult,

471
00:26:22,260 --> 00:26:23,300
let's verify

472
00:26:23,300 --> 00:26:24,820
the extent of her injury.

473
00:26:30,580 --> 00:26:31,420
Yes.

474
00:26:31,780 --> 00:26:32,620
Come.

475
00:26:33,060 --> 00:26:34,460
Let me go!

476
00:26:34,780 --> 00:26:36,740
I only said

477
00:26:36,740 --> 00:26:38,140
the young master kissed

478
00:26:38,140 --> 00:26:39,220
and touched me.

479
00:26:39,220 --> 00:26:40,380
Absurd!

480
00:26:41,300 --> 00:26:43,740
Can only extreme acts be counted as vile?

481
00:26:43,980 --> 00:26:45,140
No matter what,

482
00:26:45,140 --> 00:26:47,620
the young master still harassed me.

483
00:26:49,860 --> 00:26:50,700
Cuiliu,

484
00:26:51,020 --> 00:26:52,260
I know

485
00:26:52,260 --> 00:26:53,380
about you and Su Jue.

486
00:26:53,940 --> 00:26:55,380
The villain is already struggling.

487
00:26:55,620 --> 00:26:56,660
Do you think

488
00:26:57,060 --> 00:26:59,620
bringing up the Su family will save you?

489
00:27:00,820 --> 00:27:03,380
Do you think
the Su family will let you go?

490
00:27:08,460 --> 00:27:09,340
Your Lordship,

491
00:27:09,340 --> 00:27:10,500
this may involve...

492
00:27:10,500 --> 00:27:11,340
It was me.

493
00:27:11,540 --> 00:27:12,460
I did it.

494
00:27:12,860 --> 00:27:15,340
I couldn't stand that wretch being happy,

495
00:27:15,340 --> 00:27:16,620
so I did this.

496
00:27:16,620 --> 00:27:17,980
Outrageous!

497
00:27:18,220 --> 00:27:19,220
In the perfume case,

498
00:27:19,220 --> 00:27:20,860
I showed leniency
because you were coerced

499
00:27:20,860 --> 00:27:23,820
and the Pei family pleaded.

500
00:27:23,820 --> 00:27:25,340
I didn't give you a heavy sentence,

501
00:27:25,780 --> 00:27:28,060
yet you haven't repented

502
00:27:28,060 --> 00:27:29,300
and have worsened.

503
00:27:29,300 --> 00:27:31,180
Guards, take her away!

504
00:27:32,620 --> 00:27:34,540
Your Lordship, spare me!

505
00:27:34,780 --> 00:27:35,700
- Your Lordship!
- Move.

506
00:27:35,700 --> 00:27:36,660
I was wrong.

507
00:27:36,980 --> 00:27:38,420
I was truly wrong.

508
00:27:38,780 --> 00:27:39,980
Let me go!

509
00:27:39,980 --> 00:27:40,860
Your Lordship,

510
00:27:40,860 --> 00:27:42,460
can I take the young master home now?

511
00:27:43,740 --> 00:27:44,580
Yes.

512
00:27:48,980 --> 00:27:49,820
Be careful.

513
00:27:50,060 --> 00:27:50,980
Slowly.

514
00:27:55,300 --> 00:27:56,140
Come on.

515
00:27:57,460 --> 00:27:58,300
Here.

516
00:28:29,380 --> 00:28:30,740
Watch your wound.

517
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:32,660
It doesn't hurt.

518
00:28:34,540 --> 00:28:35,460
Thank you

519
00:28:36,300 --> 00:28:37,220
for being so considerate

520
00:28:37,980 --> 00:28:39,500
this time.

521
00:28:41,540 --> 00:28:42,380
I know.

522
00:28:42,940 --> 00:28:45,140
You don't want your mother to worry,

523
00:28:45,940 --> 00:28:47,060
so I had to ensure you

524
00:28:47,060 --> 00:28:48,460
return with dignity.

525
00:28:53,300 --> 00:28:54,540
Does the wound still hurt?

526
00:28:55,340 --> 00:28:56,300
It doesn't.

527
00:29:00,220 --> 00:29:01,060
That day,

528
00:29:01,780 --> 00:29:03,340
in the library,

529
00:29:03,740 --> 00:29:04,780
I spoke harshly

530
00:29:05,140 --> 00:29:06,420
out of impulse.

531
00:29:07,580 --> 00:29:08,420
Sorry.

532
00:29:10,500 --> 00:29:11,540
It's nothing.

533
00:29:11,780 --> 00:29:13,260
I was a bit reckless too.

534
00:29:13,620 --> 00:29:14,620
We're even.

535
00:29:19,740 --> 00:29:21,020
Were you angry

536
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:24,140
about the Cuiliu incident at first?

537
00:29:25,940 --> 00:29:27,140
At first,

538
00:29:27,140 --> 00:29:28,380
I was furious,

539
00:29:28,380 --> 00:29:30,380
wondering how you could be so foolish.

540
00:29:32,620 --> 00:29:34,100
But I only stayed angry for a while.

541
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:35,300
Then I just wanted

542
00:29:35,620 --> 00:29:37,660
to get you out, no matter what.

543
00:29:39,780 --> 00:29:41,140
I can't lose you.

544
00:29:43,940 --> 00:29:44,780
Dandan,

545
00:29:46,460 --> 00:29:47,740
when I was in prison,

546
00:29:49,260 --> 00:29:50,340
I was terrified.

547
00:29:50,860 --> 00:29:52,300
Not of punishment

548
00:29:52,360 --> 00:29:53,500
or death.

549
00:29:54,220 --> 00:29:55,180
I was afraid

550
00:29:55,540 --> 00:29:57,140
of never seeing you again.

551
00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:01,340
Alright.

552
00:30:01,540 --> 00:30:03,300
Don't think about that anymore.

553
00:30:03,300 --> 00:30:05,060
You're seeing me now, aren't you?

554
00:30:05,060 --> 00:30:07,460
And you'll see me every day from now on.

555
00:30:09,460 --> 00:30:10,660
You said it.

556
00:30:10,860 --> 00:30:12,060
Every day from now on.

557
00:30:12,060 --> 00:30:13,220
Not a single day less.

558
00:30:13,860 --> 00:30:14,940
Every day, indeed.

559
00:30:21,820 --> 00:30:22,700
I love you.

560
00:30:30,940 --> 00:30:31,940
I love you too.

561
