00:30:54,580 --> 00:30:56,460
Madam, Madam!

563
00:30:56,780 --> 00:30:58,260
- Liu.
- Young Master is back!

564
00:30:58,500 --> 00:30:59,340
He's back!

565
00:31:00,300 --> 00:31:01,700
- Ms. Li.
- Madam.

566
00:31:03,340 --> 00:31:04,180
Pei!

567
00:31:06,540 --> 00:31:07,380
Mother.

