00:31:13,220 --> 00:31:14,300
You've suffered.

571
00:31:15,380 --> 00:31:16,220
Not really.

572
00:31:17,940 --> 00:31:20,220
Dandan, you did it.

573
00:31:23,540 --> 00:31:25,460
Go rest inside now.

574
00:31:27,060 --> 00:31:29,420
Madam Pei, greetings.

575
00:31:33,220 --> 00:31:34,260
What are you doing here?

576
00:31:35,020 --> 00:31:36,700
I heard Pei was severely injured,

577
00:31:37,060 --> 00:31:38,500
so I came to check on him.

578
00:31:39,300 --> 00:31:41,900
Unexpectedly, he still looks vigorous.

579
00:31:43,300 --> 00:31:44,820
All thanks to you.

580
00:31:45,140 --> 00:31:46,340
What do you mean by that?

581
00:31:46,620 --> 00:31:47,980
I don't understand.

582
00:31:50,500 --> 00:31:52,340
I saw Cuiliu getting into your carriage.

583
00:31:52,540 --> 00:31:53,660
You've been causing trouble

584
00:31:54,020 --> 00:31:55,740
all along, haven't you?

585
00:31:56,860 --> 00:31:57,900
That girl?

586
00:31:58,780 --> 00:32:00,980
I saw her being thrown out,

587
00:32:01,860 --> 00:32:03,060
so I took her in

588
00:32:03,060 --> 00:32:04,340
out of pity.

589
00:32:04,580 --> 00:32:06,020
As for what you're saying,

590
00:32:06,300 --> 00:32:08,060
aren't you overthinking it?

591
00:32:08,380 --> 00:32:10,180
Using such despicable methods,

592
00:32:10,540 --> 00:32:12,740
there's no need to stir up trouble here.

593
00:32:25,140 --> 00:32:26,780
Ms. Shuangshuang, how are you?

594
00:32:27,700 --> 00:32:28,900
What's it to you?

595
00:32:29,260 --> 00:32:30,540
Who are you

596
