- to speak here?
- You...

597
00:32:32,220 --> 00:32:34,020
Mr. Su, mind your own business.

598
00:32:36,300 --> 00:32:37,420
You're not welcome here.

599
00:32:38,100 --> 00:32:39,660
Liu, show him out.

600
00:32:39,940 --> 00:32:40,780
Yes.

601
00:32:41,780 --> 00:32:43,660
Mr. Su, please.

602
00:32:43,980 --> 00:32:44,860
What's the hurry?

603
00:32:45,940 --> 00:32:47,100
It will take you thirty years

604
00:32:47,100 --> 00:32:48,500
to turn things around.

605
00:32:48,940 --> 00:32:50,820
At least thirty years.

606
00:32:51,220 --> 00:32:52,180
Mr. Pei,

607
00:32:53,060 --> 00:32:54,660
