610
00:33:01,020 --> 00:33:01,940
Here.

611
00:33:01,940 --> 00:33:02,820
Mr. Su.

612
00:33:03,540 --> 00:33:04,540
Here.

613
00:33:08,140 --> 00:33:09,220
Sit, Mr. Qin.

614
00:33:10,700 --> 00:33:11,620
Is it convenient?

615
00:33:12,780 --> 00:33:13,820
Thank you, Mr. Su.

616
00:33:17,300 --> 00:33:18,860
Mr. Qin, you're smiling

617
00:33:18,860 --> 00:33:20,180
quite ominously today.

618
00:33:20,780 --> 00:33:22,340
What are you talking about?

619
00:33:22,340 --> 00:33:25,540
The Jade Shop relies entirely on you.

620
00:33:25,540 --> 00:33:27,500
Now, with the Pei family in trouble,

621
00:33:27,820 --> 00:33:29,860
who doesn't treat you

622
00:33:29,860 --> 00:33:32,580
as a master, Mr. Su?

623
00:33:32,580 --> 00:33:33,820
Mr. Qin, let me ask you.

624
00:33:34,300 --> 00:33:35,780
How often does your store

625
00:33:35,780 --> 00:33:37,180
get new stock?

626
00:33:37,940 --> 00:33:41,300
The journey is long.
Once every six months.

627
00:33:41,300 --> 00:33:43,020
If I bought out

628
00:33:43,020 --> 00:33:43,980
all your raw stones,

629
00:33:44,740 --> 00:33:46,420
wouldn't others be unable to buy any?

630
00:33:47,500 --> 00:33:49,740
If you bought all my stones,

631
00:33:49,740 --> 00:33:50,940
thanks to you,

632
00:33:50,940 --> 00:33:52,820
I'd be able to take a holiday.

633
00:33:53,500 --> 00:33:55,020
Then I'll make it happen.

634
00:33:56,100 --> 00:33:58,020
Thank you, Mr. Su.

635
00:33:58,020 --> 00:33:58,940
You two, take your time.

636
00:33:58,940 --> 00:33:59,900
I'll make arrangements.

637
00:34:01,380 --> 00:34:02,460
Jue,

638
00:34:02,780 --> 00:34:04,940
are you really going
to buy all the raw stones

639
00:34:04,940 --> 00:34:05,820
in the area?

640
00:34:06,460 --> 00:34:09,580
If you do,
our treasury will be nearly empty.

641
00:34:10,340 --> 00:34:11,620
Think it through.

642
00:34:11,980 --> 00:34:13,180
I've thought it through.

643
00:34:13,900 --> 00:34:15,100
You're right.

644
00:34:15,540 --> 00:34:17,380
Without the Qipei Pavilion,

645
00:34:17,740 --> 00:34:19,300
where else can the beauty go?

646
00:34:19,540 --> 00:34:20,940
This is a fight

647
00:34:22,540 --> 00:34:23,860
to the death.

648
00:34:24,860 --> 00:34:26,740
Yes.

649
00:34:26,740 --> 00:34:27,780
Let's buy them all.

650
00:34:32,580 --> 00:34:33,620
What do you mean?

651
00:34:33,900 --> 00:34:35,140
Speak clearly.

652
00:34:38,380 --> 00:34:39,940
Madam, Young Master.

653
00:34:40,940 --> 00:34:41,780
Bad news!

654
00:34:41,860 --> 00:34:42,700
What happened?

655
00:34:42,700 --> 00:34:45,020
Suyu Pavilion suddenly
started selling goods at half price.

656
00:34:45,020 --> 00:34:46,460
Our Qipei Pavilion's shops

657
00:34:47,060 --> 00:34:48,380
are all deserted.

658
00:34:48,380 --> 00:34:49,900
Then we'll reduce our prices by 30%.

659
