00:35:19,220 --> 00:35:21,060
Why do they buy so many raw stones?

673
00:35:21,060 --> 00:35:22,500
Aren't they afraid of overstocking?

674
00:35:22,980 --> 00:35:23,900
Not at all.

675
00:35:24,140 --> 00:35:25,340
Such a grand scheme.

676
00:35:25,340 --> 00:35:27,420
They want to fight us to the death.

677
00:35:27,940 --> 00:35:30,020
Whether they lose or not,

678
00:35:30,020 --> 00:35:32,740
